Mereka ingat boleh bawa kemungkinan baharu
untuk nyawa, ketenteraan dan kehidupan.

244
00:17:17,250 --> 00:17:17,979
Dia ada pistol.

245
00:17:17,980 --> 00:17:18,629
Wang Xiaoxiu.

246
00:17:18,630 --> 00:17:21,149
Melalui eksperimen
gabungan gen biologi kami,

247
00:17:21,150 --> 00:17:23,859
penguatan super badan manusia
dah tercapai.

248
00:17:23,880 --> 00:17:25,410
Saya tak boleh mati lagi...

249
00:17:25,970 --> 00:17:29,470
Mari kita lihat siapa yang mati dulu.

250
00:17:30,690 --> 00:17:31,820
Awak tiada apa-apa?

251
00:17:36,140 --> 00:17:37,420
♪ Seperti satu mimpi ♪

252
00:17:39,260 --> 00:17:42,270
♪ Ingin sentuhmu tapi terjatuh ♪

253
00:17:42,600 --> 00:17:44,240
♪ Dalam lautan manusia ♪

254
00:17:45,740 --> 00:17:49,300
♪ Seperti ditolak ke dalam pusaran yang tiada batasan ♪

255
00:17:49,380 --> 00:17:54,260
♪ Aku yang berada di luar sinaranmu ♪

256
00:17:54,340 --> 00:17:57,780
♪ Bagaimana mendekatimu dan menyampaikan ♪

257
00:17:57,880 --> 00:18:03,500
♪ Suara rindu itu ♪

258
00:18:03,580 --> 00:18:06,500
♪ Dah tak sempat ♪

259
00:18:06,540 --> 00:18:14,639
♪ Cerita sampai ke sini, hanya tinggal aku seorang ♪

260
00:18:14,640 --> 00:18:16,000
♪ Kelopak bunga yang berterbang ♪

261
00:18:17,680 --> 00:18:21,320
♪ Bagaikan kekesalan yang tak dipenuhi ♪

262
00:18:27,060 --> 00:18:30,360
♪ Sebelum langit berbintang gelap ♪

263
00:18:30,800 --> 00:18:34,900
♪ Bolehkah aku melihatmu sekali lagi?♪

264
00:18:35,760 --> 00:18:39,940
♪ Walaupun kau takkan perasan ♪

265
00:18:40,100 --> 00:18:43,380
♪ Kenangan terdampar di dada ♪

266
00:18:43,600 --> 00:18:46,600
♪ Tiba-tiba jatuh ke dalam jurang ♪

267
00:18:46,840 --> 00:18:48,420
♪ Aku pejamkan mata ♪

268
00:18:48,560 --> 00:18:52,160
♪ Tak sanggup melihat masa silam muncul semula ♪

269
00:18:52,940 --> 00:18:56,100
♪ Ucapkan selamat tinggal ♪

270
00:18:56,160 --> 00:18:58,540
♪ Masih bermundar-mandir ♪

271
00:18:59,280 --> 00:19:02,160
♪ Macam mana aku boleh?♪

272
00:19:02,420 --> 00:19:05,320
♪ Lepaskan tangan dan rasa lega ♪

273
00:19:05,580 --> 00:19:08,180
♪ Ucapkan selamat tinggal ♪

274
00:19:08,660 --> 00:19:11,720
♪ Pergi tanpa memiliki apa-apa ♪

275
00:19:12,100 --> 00:19:14,500
♪ Di manakah cahayaku?♪

276
00:19:15,000 --> 00:19:18,100
♪ Tinggal saja kekosongan di depan mata ♪

